{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a clearance products section that displays products in a responsive grid layout. On mobile, show 2x2 grid (4 products total). On desktop, show 2x4 grid (8 products total). Each product should have a quick "add to cart" button for immediate purchasing. Include a "View All" button that links to the complete clearance collection. Add horizontal shaking animation for promotional messaging to highlight special offers and limited-time deals. Make the section highly customizable with options for colors, text, spacing, and layout adjustments. The section should have a clearance/sale vibe with appropriate styling.

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

